description: This Chainlink VRF common Anurak purrs with a rating of 43, and a multiplier of 1x. It has a total score of 43, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Stringalong for North, 2 for East, Nine Lives for South, and Leverage for West. Anurak has the personality suit of hodler. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random packs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Anurak [43 Votes, Common]
